The paper deals with autonomous driving and lane detection, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed solution involves the use of deep learning architectures, which is a common theme in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of attention mechanisms, which is a popular research area in natural language processing (cs.CL). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.CL.
